snippet.title: The Fan - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
THE FAN is an upcoming interactive photo fiction with real locations and actors. It will be release first on PC, early 2017.

Please, also check The Fan Cinematic Teaser:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g8WHQvBb-iI

Check out the official website : http://thefan-game.blogspot.fr/
You can also like the game on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/thefangame
and follow it on Twitter: https://twitter.com/Cyril_Danon

Music Credits:

"Bump in the Night" Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com) 
Licensed under Creative Commons: By Attribution 3.0
http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/

"Very Low Note" Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com) 
Licensed under Creative Commons: By Attribution 3.0
http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/

Sound FX by Joshua Crispin aka Generdyn
http://99sounds.org/cinematic-sound-effects/
